WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.760
I'd definitely recommend someone, whether a beginner, intermediate or advanced, to come

00:00:10.760 --> 00:00:13.480
to RStudioConf.

00:00:13.480 --> 00:00:19.559
I would recommend it for anyone that is either learning R, using R, an expert in R. I've been

00:00:19.559 --> 00:00:21.639
using R for almost 15 years.

00:00:21.639 --> 00:00:25.400
Every year I've come, I've learned at least two or three things I'd never heard of.

